@AccessCity.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005

### HEALTH
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### AUTHENTICATION (AuthController)

### register user
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

### login user
# @name login
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### read token
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### refresh token
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### revoke token
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/revoke-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### forgot password
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### reset password
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "token": "YOUR_RESET_TOKEN_HERE",
  "newPassword": "newPassword123"
}

### MAP TILES (MapTileController)

### GET Map Tile (Requires Auth)
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/tiles/1/1/1.pbf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### SPATIAL (SpatialController)

### GET Points of Interest
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/spatial/poi?lat=52.4862&lng=-1.8904&radius=1000
Accept: application/json

### GET Map Overlay (Hazards)
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/spatial/map-overlay?layerName=hazards
Accept: application/json

### GET Map Overlay (Infrastructure)
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/spatial/map-overlay?layerName=infrastructure
Accept: application/json

### ROUTING (RoutingController)

### POST Safe Path
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/routing/safe-path
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": { "x": -1.8904, "y": 52.4862 },
  "end": { "x": -1.8894, "y": 52.4862 },
  "profile": "wheelchair",
  "safetyWeight": 0.8
}

### GET Risk Score
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/routing/risk-score?lat=52.4862&lng=-1.8904&radius=500
Accept: application/json

### GET AI Risk Score
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/routing/ai-risk-score?lat=52.4862&lng=-1.8904&radius=200
Accept: application/json

### HAZARDS (HazardsController)

### GET Hazards
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/hazards?minLat=52.4&minLng=-2.0&maxLat=52.6&maxLng=-1.8
Accept: application/json

### POST Report Hazard
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/hazards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Broken Pavement",
  "description": "Large crack making wheelchair access difficult",
  "location": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [-1.8904, 52.4862]
  },
  "source": "user"
}

### GET Hazard by ID
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/hazards/YOUR_HAZARD_GUID_HERE
Accept: application/json

### PATCH Update Hazard Status
PATCH {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/hazards/YOUR_HAZARD_GUID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### GEOCODING (GeocodingController)

### GET Search
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/geocoding/search?query=Birmingham%20New%20Street
Accept: application/json

### GET Reverse Geocoding
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/geocoding/reverse?lat=52.4778&lon=-1.8983
Accept: application/json

### OFFLINE MAP (OfflineMapController)

### GET Offline Map Bundle (Requires Auth)
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/offlinemap/bundle?minLat=52.4&minLng=-2.0&maxLat=52.6&maxLng=-1.8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### DASHBOARD (DashboardController)

### GET Dashboard Summary
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/summary
Accept: application/json

### GET Dashboard Heat Map
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/heat-map
Accept: application/json

### GET Dashboard Infrastructure Feed
GET {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/infrastructure-feed?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### ADMIN OSM (AdminOsmController)

### POST Import OSM
POST {{AccessCity.API_HostAddress}}/api/admin/osm/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

